ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 192, Saskatchewan
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 192 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the provision of financial assistance to the province of SASKATCHEWAN, with respect to the HEAVY RAINFALL, that affected the province, from June 18, 2014 to June 21, 2014.
